Cut it out!

352
00:13:46,702 --> 00:13:48,635
And you can be Hector.
Now get over there.

353
00:13:48,637 --> 00:13:49,770
I'm taking Ferb.

354
00:13:49,772 --> 00:13:51,972
Hey everyone, can I play?
BUFORD: No!

355
00:13:51,974 --> 00:13:53,607
I've got baklava.

356
00:13:53,609 --> 00:13:55,342
Welcome to the
Greek army.

357
00:13:55,344 --> 00:13:57,878
You know who loves history
and historical reenactments.

358
00:13:57,880 --> 00:13:59,746
Hey, where's
your dad?

359
00:14:00,548 --> 00:14:01,949
DAD: So it goes over,

360
00:14:01,951 --> 00:14:03,851
under, around and through.

361
00:14:03,853 --> 00:14:05,652
(INHALES)
Oh, lovely.

362
00:14:05,654 --> 00:14:07,120
Time to open the shop.

363
00:14:14,929 --> 00:14:16,096
(RINGING)

364
00:14:17,065 --> 00:14:18,365
(BRAYING)

