00:15:17,025 --> 00:15:18,725
Yeah, we're gonna need
a bigger army.

385
00:15:18,727 --> 00:15:20,827
Irving, break out my
recruitin' fustanella.

386
00:15:20,829 --> 00:15:21,995
You mean the
little Greek skirt?

387
00:15:21,997 --> 00:15:23,430
It's a fustanella!

